{"tid":1229551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[清泉] 集合有表態嘅香港youtuber","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T09:18:32.000Z","uid":9624,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3195bce579d689ba552fb06cfccf63ff1bf84b","tid":1229551,"uid":9624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"當好多明星或者公眾人物會選擇唔出聲甚至繼續飲飲食食時，<br />\n好多謝你地仲願意透過公眾平台去發聲，<br />\n唔知最後會點，唔知你地會唔會俾人ban片，甚至將來有手尾，<br />\n但希望以後大家都會記得有你地，為自由同公義發聲，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdW7pEUV4H0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrdW7pEUV4H0&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=ff81ce3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdW7pEUV4H0</a><br />\n你雖然係外國/混血兒，但你係真・香港人！多謝你！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oylVk6eB5vA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoylVk6eB5vA&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=79a3cbf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oylVk6eB5vA</a><br />\n我都同好多連登仔一樣有笑過你，對唔住，但你值得尊重！多謝你！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lglyJvgHeWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlglyJvgHeWQ&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=570d919d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lglyJvgHeWQ</a><br />\nBOB叔一早已經上了神枱，但都係要提一提每次呢D政治議題你都唔會避嫌，甚至帶頭討論，多謝你！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWt4PRai58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaWt4PRai58w&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=2749d9e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWt4PRai58w</a><br />\n成日睇你開心煮飯仔，冇諗過你會出聲，多謝你！<br />\n<br />\n由於標題都講咗係香港youtuber，所以就唔講台灣/日本了。<br />\n如果仲有其他嘅都歡迎各位補充，感激各位出力，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我希望有一日就算網路上都消失哂，我地都會記得。</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa46d2025930d0a2cf2adafaf95c5568d019c0dc","tid":1229551,"uid":251736,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"仲有 rock 哥"},{"pid":"5741d94e9cdc5140cdc6f65cc36bf82dc77f5abc","tid":1229551,"uid":236073,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9704ff8b31c81d5640b2c3ad2465b5fdd9f402b3","tid":1229551,"uid":249971,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"大j"},{"pid":"37ed4c66331f846f424ce7fab53bbea57265e014","tid":1229551,"uid":249971,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2lSXCNLejvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2lSXCNLejvU&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=96986596\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2lSXCNLejvU</a><br />\n大丁<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JiEfq_p7GYU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJiEfq_p7GYU&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=6cfda1a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JiEfq_p7GYU</a><br />\n伍公子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mr5lvo2J8FU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmr5lvo2J8FU&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=c717c628\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mr5lvo2J8FU</a><br />\narhotv"},{"pid":"1e3a270260439383367806ed7d7135816518ea9d","tid":1229551,"uid":164336,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"Benja &amp; Momo Channel<br />\n一直有表態 有去遊行<br />\n今日好似帶埋個日本妹老婆去"},{"pid":"f1ff018eb0b3a6a34374183e5dc8258fc64d0fb8","tid":1229551,"uid":208486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"肥蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\